_sText:
players mix is a mini game where is probably that a player of the other team spawn in your spawn, and next to kill him, you have to go for the other enemies.

For a better experience it's better to play this map with 12//14 players.

When there aren't much players left, you can use all the rest of the map.

In the middle of the CT and T portal there is a hidden TOP portal.

In the upper grid there are a sig550, m4a1, g3 and ak47

In the TOP there is a AWP

In the initial grid there are two P90 and two scout

Songs: Evanescense - Bring me to life

             Joel Nielsen - Questionable ethics

             Linkin Park - In the end

             Skillet - Never Surrender
